005package edu.wpi.first.hal.simulation;
006
007import edu.wpi.first.hal.JNIWrapper;
008
009public class PowerDistributionDataJNI extends JNIWrapper {
010  public static native int registerInitializedCallback(
011      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
012
013  public static native void cancelInitializedCallback(int index, int uid);
014
015  public static native boolean getInitialized(int index);
016
017  public static native void setInitialized(int index, boolean initialized);
018
019  public static native int registerTemperatureCallback(
020      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
021
022  public static native void cancelTemperatureCallback(int index, int uid);
023
024  public static native double getTemperature(int index);
025
026  public static native void setTemperature(int index, double temperature);
027
028  public static native int registerVoltageCallback(
029      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
030
031  public static native void cancelVoltageCallback(int index, int uid);
032
033  public static native double getVoltage(int index);
034
035  public static native void setVoltage(int index, double voltage);
036
037  public static native int registerCurrentCallback(
038      int index, int channel, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
039
040  public static native void cancelCurrentCallback(int index, int channel, int uid);
041
042  public static native double getCurrent(int index, int channel);
043
044  public static native void setCurrent(int index, int channel, double current);
045
046  public static native void resetData(int index);
047}
